    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>orzo</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the dish and gently stir it all together</p>",
