    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for 20-25 min or until the liquid has been absorbed and the orzo is cooked – this is your <strong>oven-baked orzo</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p>",
