    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Add most of the <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong>, <strong>chopped basil</strong> and <strong>rocket</strong> (save some of each for garnish!) to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>rocket pesto</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don't have a food processor, use a pestle & mortar!</p>",
