      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>oven-baked orzo</strong> with the <strong>roasted aubergine & tomato</strong> – this is your <strong>roasted aubergine & tomato orzo</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>roasted aubergine & tomato orzo </strong>with the <strong>rocket pesto</strong> drizzled all over</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped basil</strong>, <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong> and <strong>rocket</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
